OL,2,                       k                
OL,3,                                  Q "###
OL,4,C Hostile powers have enacted a cowardly
OL,5,C blockade on medical supplies. To      
OL,6,C ensure our brave border peace-keepers 
OL,7,C survive enforcement injuries,         
OL,8,C Xenoxxx is now SELF-RELIANT in iodine 
OL,9,C production.                           
OL,11,  CITIZEN KELP COLLECTION:FAll able-    
OL,12,F bodied residents must report to       
OL,13,F coastal sectors. Collected seaweed is 
OL,14,F to be delivered to the BURNING PITS   
OL,15,F for chemical extraction.              
OL,17,  ANTISEPTIC STOCKS:FIodine is vital for
OL,18,F wound care management at the front    
OL,19, Flines.                                
OL,20,F                                       
OL,21,  COLLECTION QUOTA:F50kg per household  
OL,22,F weekly. Failure is a lack of spirit.  
OL,23,         Safety warnings follow----->1/2
